{"tid":2413872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[網絡安全警告] 針對通訊軟件的釣魚式詐騙","createTime":"2021-02-19T04:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T13:04:12.000Z","uid":246823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed63f5336161611c3d61f2ac09a3cd45dfa6126","tid":2413872,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"HK Infosec 察覺到最近社交網絡上流行一種釣魚欺詐手法，目的是盜取 Facebook 登入名稱及密碼<br />\n請各位務必小心，在通訊軟件內按下任何連結、圖片或影片之前請提高警覺。<br />\n<br />\n是次欺詐名為 &quot;Look what I found&quot;, 曾一度流行於 2020 年 9 月至 10月期間。騙徒會用通訊軟件向目標傳送一條連結(看似是一段影片), 按下後會轉跳至假冒 Facebook 登入面頁, 所輸入的登入資料會傳送至騙徒的伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n騙徒獲得登入資料後就會嘗試登入目標人士的帳戶，成功後或會再向受害人的聯絡人發送同樣的連結，以獲取更多帳戶的登入資料 (login credentials)<br />\n<br />\n圖為通訊軟件 facebook messenger, 可見騙徒盜取帳號後向受害人某個群組發送連結<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPNog0s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPNog0s.png&h=43441ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHK Infosec 義工分析是次假冒Facebook 登入頁面的代碼，發現所輸入資料會傳送至一個叫 sociallands club 的網域<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47JCms6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47JCms6.png&h=db38964b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是次詐騙中所使用的其中兩個檔案<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGYe79b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGYe79b.png&h=a995d79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細技術分析及完整代碼可在此下載 (需同意使用條款) <br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/group/602eb84535036302d952cbec/documents\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fgroup%2F602eb84535036302d952cbec%2Fdocuments&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69GjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=349defaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/group/602eb84535036302d952cbec/documents</a><br />\n<br />\n同步發送<br />\n軟件台, 時事台"},{"pid":"bf591f3a94986207c7c4d3c7521186231cae80e3","tid":2413872,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70f17a54f9e2f0e37e9355867c8537312e6e25e","tid":2413872,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:36:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61d74781ab1d1e13cbf25e51f101e59a6bf34e4","tid":2413872,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}